snippet.title: Clash Of Evil Full Trailer 2016
snippet.description:
The biggest, deadliest, battle we've all anticipated is finally here! Your favorite scary character is now available to play on mobile devices! Take on the best of the best in Clash Of Evil, coming out soon for both the App Store and Play Store! Keep in the loop for constant updates and awards!
